te ble Amandavinnerne 2018|url=http://www.kinomagasinet.no/artikkel/dette-ble-amandavinnerne-2018/|website=Kinomagasinet|date=18 August  2018|accessdate=21 September 2018|language=Norwegian|quote=(These are Amanda Winners 2018)}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Director\n| {{sort|Trier|Joachim Trier}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Actress\n| {{sort|Harboe|Eili Harboe}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Actor\n| Henrik Rafaelsen\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Supporting Actress\n| Kaya Wilkins\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Screenplay\n| {{sort|Vogt|Eskil Vogt}}, {{sort|Trier|Joachim Trier}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Cinematography\n| Jakob Ihre\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Production Design/Scenography\n| Roger Rosenberg\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Visual Effects\n| Esben Syberg (Shortcut)\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Music\n| Ola Fl\u00f8ttum\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Editing\n| Olivier Bugge Coutts\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Sound Design\n| Gisle Tveito\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=1| [[Nordic Council Film Prize]]\n| rowspan=1| <center>30 October 2018</center>\n| Award\n| ''Thelma''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last1=NTB|title=Triers \u00abThelma\u00bb norsk kandidat til Nordisk r\u00e5ds filmpris 2018|url=https://www.smp.no/ntb/innenriks/2018/08/21/Triers-\u00abThelma\u00bb-norsk-kandidat-til-Nordisk-r\u00e5ds-filmpris-2018-17368086.ece|work=[[Sunnm\u00f8rsposten]]|date=21 August 2018|accessdate=21 September 2018|language=Norwegian|quote=(Trier's \"Thelma\" Norwegian Candidate for the Nordic Council Film Prize 2018)}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of LGBT-related films]]\n* [[Lists of Norwegian films]]\n* [[List of Norwegian submissions for the Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film]]\n* [[List of submissions to the 90th Academy Awards for Best Foreign Language Film]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Further reading==\n<!-- If a source in this section is used in the article as a citation: remove from list. -->\n\n* {{cite web|last1=Avella|first1=Frank J.|title=Talking 'Thelma' with Joachim Trier - Supernatural Lesbian Love in Norway|url=https://www.edgemedianetwork.com/entertainment/movies/252199|website=EDGE Media Network|publisher=EDGE Publications, Inc.|date=17 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Bramesco|first1= Charles|title=Meet The Stars Of \u2018Thelma,\u2019 The Lesbian Horror Movie Everyone Is Talking About|url=https://nylon.com/articles/thelma-lesbian-horror-movie-interviews|website=[[Nylon (magazine)|Nylon]]|date=12 September 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1= Foutch|first1=Haleigh|title=\u2018Thelma\u2019 Director Joachim Trier on How His Supernatural Thriller Transformed into a Queer Love Story|url=http://collider.com/joachim-trier-thelma-interview/|website=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|date=17 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Ganjavie|first1=Amir|title=Interview: Joachim Trier \u2013 Thelma|url=https://www.ioncinema.com/interviews/joachim-trier-thelma|website=IONCINEMA.com|date=18 December 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Grobar|first1=Matt|title=\u2018Thelma\u2019 Director Joachim Trier On Norway\u2019s \"Visceral, Visual & Erotic\" Oscar Selection \u2014 Toronto Studio|url=https://deadline.com/2017/09/thelma-joachim-trier-eili-harboe-toronto-film-festival-video-1202167218/|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=13 September 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Hall|first1=Jacob|title=\u2018Thelma\u2019 Director Joachim Trier on Crafting His Incredible Queer Horror Film [Interview]|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/thelma-director-interview/|website=[[/Film]]|date=23 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Handler|first1=Rachel|title=Thelma\u2019s Joachim Trier on Filming Lesbian Sex Scenes Sans the Male Gaze and Subverting Stereotypes|url=http://www.vulture.com/2017/11/thelmas-joachim-trier-on-his-strange-erotic-thriller.html|website=[[New York (magazine)|Vulture]]|date=10 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Iversen|first1=Kristin|title=How \u2018Thelma\u2019 Destroys The Soft Power And Perversity Of The Patriarchy