 2017|url=http://www.houstonfilmcritics.org/awards.php|website=[[Houston Film Critics Society]]|date=2018|accessdate=29 September 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Roberts|first1=James|title=\u2018Lady Bird\u2019 Wins Big at 11th Annual Houston Film Critics Society Awards|url=https://glidemagazine.com/198491/lady-bird-wins-big-11th-annual-houston-film-critics-society-awards/|website=Glide Magazine|date=8 January 2018|accessdate=29 September 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=1| [[Critics' Choice Movie Awards]]\n| rowspan=1| <center>[[23rd Critics' Choice Awards|11 January 2018]]</center>\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]]\n| ''Thelma''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=TapleyCCA>{{cite web|last1=Tapley|first1=Kristopher|title=\u2018Shape of Water\u2019 Leads Critics\u2019 Choice Film Nominations|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/awards/critics-choice-film-nominations-list-1202631789/|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=6 December 2017|accessdate=24 June 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"TimesCCA\">{{cite web|title=Complete list of nominees and winners for the 23rd Critics' Choice Awards|url=http://envelope.latimes.com/awards/critics-choice/2018/|work=[[Los Angeles Times]]|date=20 January 2018|accessdate=24 June 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=10| [[Kosmorama|Kosmorama International Film Festival]]\n| rowspan=10| <center>8 March 2018</center>\n| Best Picture\n| ''Thelma''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=10 style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=Montages>{{cite web|title=Her er de nominerte til Kanonprisen 2018 \u2013 Thelma og Hva vil folk si leder an|url=http://montages.no/nyheter/her-er-de-nominerte-til-kanonprisen-2018-thelma-og-hva-vil-folk-si-leder-an/|website=Montages|date=8 February 2018|accessdate=29 June 2018|language=Norwegian|quote=Here are the nominees for Kanonprisen 2018 \u2013 Thelma and What Will People Say leads the way.}}</ref><ref name=Kanonprisen>{{cite web|