andaprisen 2018: Flest nominasjoner til \u00abThelma\u00bb|url=https://filmfestivalen.no/amandaprisen-2018-flest-nominasjoner-til-thelma/|website=[[Norwegian International Film Festival|Den Norske Filmfestivalen i Haugesund]]|date=20 June 2018|accessdate=24 June 2018|language=Norwegian|quote=Amanda Award 2018: Most Nominations to \"Thelma\".}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=H\u00f8kaas|first1=Christian|title=Dette ble Amandavinnerne 2018|url=http://www.kinomagasinet.no/artikkel/dette-ble-amandavinnerne-2018/|website=Kinomagasinet|date=18 August  2018|accessdate=21 September 2018|language=Norwegian|quote=(These are Amanda Winners 2018)}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Director\n| {{sort|Trier|Joachim Trier}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Actress\n| {{sort|Harboe|Eili Harboe}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Actor\n| Henrik Rafaelsen\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Supporting Actress\n| Kaya Wilkins\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Screenplay\n| {{sort|Vogt|Eskil Vogt}}, {{sort|Trier|Joachim Trier}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Cinematography\n| Jakob Ihre\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Production Design/Scenography\n| Roger Rosenberg\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Visual Effects\n| Esben Syberg (Shortcut)\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Music\n| Ola Fl\u00f8ttum\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Editing\n| Olivier Bugge Coutts\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Sound Design\n| Gisle Tveito\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=1| [[Nordic Council Film Prize]]\n| rowspan=1| <center>30 October 2018</center>\n| Award\n| ''Thelma''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last1=NTB|title=Triers \u00abThelma\u00bb norsk kandidat til Nordisk r\u00e5ds filmpris 2018|url=https://www.smp.no/ntb/innenriks/2018/08/21/Triers-\u00abThelma\u00bb-norsk-kandidat-til-Nordisk-r\u00e5ds-filmpris-2018-17368086.ece|work=[[Sunnm\u00f8rsposten]]|date=21 August 2018|accessdate=21 September 2018|language=Norwegian|quote=(Trier's \"Thelma\" Norwegian Candidate for the Nordic Council Film Prize 2018)}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of LGBT-related films]]\n*