r|first1=Rachel|title=Thelma\u2019s Joachim Trier on Filming Lesbian Sex Scenes Sans the Male Gaze and Subverting Stereotypes|url=http://www.vulture.com/2017/11/thelmas-joachim-trier-on-his-strange-erotic-thriller.html|website=[[New York (magazine)|Vulture]]|date=10 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Iversen|first1=Kristin|title=How \u2018Thelma\u2019 Destroys The Soft Power And Perversity Of The Patriarchy|url=https://nylon.com/articles/joachim-trier-interview-thelma|website=[[Nylon (magazine)|Nylon]]|date=10 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Kilkenny|first1= Katie|title=How Joachim Trier Made This Year's Coolest Queer Supernatural Thriller|url=https://psmag.com/social-justice/how-joachim-trier-made-this-years-coolest-queer-supernatural-thriller|work=[[Pacific Standard]]|publisher=[[Sara Miller McCune]]|date=13 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Maksimiuk|first1=Magdalena|title=Interview: Joachim Trier on Thelma and Organizing Chaos|url=https://www.slantmagazine.com/features/article/interview-joachim-trier-on-thelma-and-organizing-chaos|website=[[Slant Magazine]]|date=7 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=McLaughlin|first1=Katherine|title=Joachim Trier talks Thelma, horror and rooting for outsiders|url=https://www.scifinow.co.uk/interviews/joachim-trier-talks-thelma-horror-and-rooting-for-outsiders/|work=[[SciFiNow]]|publisher=Kelsey Publishing Ltd|date=3 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Pahle|first1=Rebecca|title=Power and Control: Joachim Trier adds another great to 2017's slate of LGBT films with supernatural drama 'Thelma'|url=http://www.filmjournal.com/features/power-and-control-joachim-trier-adds-another-great-2017s-slate-lgbt-films-supernatural|work=[[Film Journal International]]|publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]]|date=7 November 2017}}\n* {{cite web|last1=Robinson|first1=Tasha|title=Thelma\u2019s director explains why he made a dreamy gay coming-of-age superhero story|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/11/10/16635068/joachim-trier-thelma-interview-